data.description: This beautifully renovated residence showcases a meticulous attention to detail, boasting a main level adorned with stunning luxury vinyl plank flooring that seamlessly extends throughout the light-filled living and dining room. The kitchen offers all new stainless steel appliances, complemented by a wine refrigerator. The convenience of a laundry area featuring front-loading washer and dryer, along with a stylish half bath, enhances the functionality of this home. Step into the newly carpeted upstairs area, where a primary bedroom awaits with a spacious walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms provide flexible living spaces, and the full bath has a custom-tiled tub shower. New sliding doors and freshly painted rooms further enhance the home's aesthetic appeal. Situated in a prime location, this residence is conveniently located next to shopping, churches, and schools, all within a mile radius. A plethora of dining options, including Starbucks, Chipotle, Cava, and Tropical Smoothie, surround the area. Bowie State University is just two miles away, making this home an ideal choice for academics. Additionally, the property straddles the line between Prince George's County and Anne Arundel County, providing easy access to the Crofton shopping complex and Bowie Town Center, both just a short drive away. With its proximity to various amenities, this residence is a mere 25 minutes from BWI Airport and 20 minutes from Annapolis, Maryland, making it a strategic and accessible location. Embrace the charm of a great neighborhood, where every aspect of 7012 Race Track Road invites you to indulge in the finest in contemporary living.
